{"ID":"20260605151320-rtsvpk8","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260605151320-rtsvpk8","title":"2020年新高考Ⅰ卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260605151457"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605151337-3thsoth","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151337-3thsoth","updated":"20260605151337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"赠别郑炼赴襄阳  杜甫"}]},{"ID":"20260605151337-iovzb40","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151337-iovzb40","updated":"20260605151337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"戎马交驰际，柴门老病身。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151337-s0qad44","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151337-s0qad44","updated":"20260605151337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"把君诗过日​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"①"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，念此别惊神。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151337-77ci0oe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151337-77ci0oe","updated":"20260605151337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"地阔峨眉晚，天高岘首春​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"②"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151337-xkdhuya","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151337-xkdhuya","updated":"20260605151337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为于耆旧内​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"③"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，试觅姓庞人​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"④"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151337-5okj1za","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151337-5okj1za","updated":"20260605151337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"[注]①把：握，执。②岘首山，在襄阳。③耆旧：年高望重的人。④姓庞人：指庞德公，汉末襄阳高士。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151320-jj2kimk","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605151320-jj2kimk","updated":"20260605151433"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260605151433-luf1fon","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151433-luf1fon","updated":"20260605151433"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．下列对这首诗的理解和赏析，不正确的一项是（    ）"}]},{"ID":"20260605151433-snccmtt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151433-snccmtt","updated":"20260605151433"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．诗的首联简单交代了兵荒马乱的时代背景和诗人年老多病的艰难境况。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151433-mqi1foc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151433-mqi1foc","updated":"20260605151433"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．虽然日后仍有朋友的诗篇陪伴，但面对离别，诗人还是感到心惊神伤。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151433-zo3c684","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151433-zo3c684","updated":"20260605151433"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．诗人请郑炼在襄阳寻访庞德公那样的高士，表达了对先贤的仰慕之意。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151433-u2525oe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151433-u2525oe","updated":"20260605151433"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．全诗情感表达含蓄蕴藉，格律谨严，比较典型地体现了杜甫诗的风格。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151433-ygj8ktk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151433-ygj8ktk","updated":"20260605151433"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"16．诗的颈联写到峨眉、岘首两座山，对表达离情有何作用?请简要分析。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151320-oepvoup","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605151320-oepvoup","updated":"20260605151444"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260605151443-28kxqtm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151443-28kxqtm","updated":"20260605151444"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．B    16．①峨眉山位于蜀地，岘首山位于襄阳，二者相距遥远；②以两山相距之远代指自己与朋友远离，不舍之情见于言外。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151320-khoh5hy","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605151320-khoh5hy","updated":"20260605151457"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260605151457-q4vmbfy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151457-q4vmbfy","updated":"20260605151457"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．本题考查学生对诗词综合赏析能力。此类题综合考查诗词的形象、语言、表达技巧和思想情感等，每个选项一个考点，几乎涵盖诗词的所有内容，注意结合全诗进行分析，主要的错误是意象的含义不对，手法不准确，手法的解说和艺术效果的分析不对，语言方面主要是风格不正确，内容一般为曲解诗词意思，答题时注意仔细辨析。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151457-3fsbwzo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151457-3fsbwzo","updated":"20260605151457"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B项， “面对离别，诗人还是感到心惊神伤”有误，“念此”的“此”应结合首联中“戎马交驰际，柴门老病身”一起理解，诗人不是为离别“心惊神伤”，而是想到在此战乱时期，自己又年老多病，一别将再难相见，故此“心惊神伤”。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151457-xsj7j0s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151457-xsj7j0s","updated":"20260605151457"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选B。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151457-i3hcfjy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151457-i3hcfjy","updated":"20260605151457"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"16．本题考查学生把握意象及分析抒情方式的能力。首先要分析意象的特点以及在诗歌中有无象征寓意；其次要结合诗歌表达技巧来分析其对于抒情的作用，并结合具体内容分析诗句运用了什么抒情技巧的，有什么表达效果，或者抒发了什么情感。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151457-oc59wjh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151457-oc59wjh","updated":"20260605151457"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“峨眉”是诗人的居住地，“岘首”是襄阳庞德公隐居的地方，也是郑炼将要前往之地。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151457-miagnl6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151457-miagnl6","updated":"20260605151457"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上句“峨眉晚”，写出离别之际因天色薄暮，而诗人不得不与友人离别的依依不舍之情；下句想象友人到达襄阳，正是春光明媚之时，表达对友人一帆风顺抵达目的地的美好祝愿；体现了诗人对友人深厚的友情。用“地阔”“天高”刻画出峨眉与岘首两座山相距遥远，借景抒情，抒发离别之后两人分居两地，相隔遥远的孤独寂寞之情"}]},{"ID":"20260605151320-lioqb3k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151320-lioqb3k","updated":"20260605142207"}}]}